de.fhg.iml.vlog.xfvrp.base.fleximport
Class CustomerData

java.lang.Object
  de.fhg.iml.vlog.xfvrp.base.fleximport.DepotData
      de.fhg.iml.vlog.xfvrp.base.fleximport.CustomerData
Direct Known Subclasses:
InternalCustomerData
public abstract class CustomerData
extends DepotData

The CustomerData is the interface to external user of the XFVRP suite. Each field in this class can be used for later optimization. Not every combination of data leads to a reasonable solution. So be aware of that. CustomerData is also responsible for the flexi import. Hereby a suite user can import data to the XFVRP suite adaptively. Not all parameters has to be filled.

Author:
hschneid
